msgstr "ÜBERSICHT"

#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux fedora-rawhide mageia-cauldron opensuse-leap-15-3
msgid "B<shutdown> [OPTIONS...] [TIME] [WALL...]"
msgstr "B<shutdown> [OPTIONEN…] [ZEIT] [WALL…]"

